title: UNESCO World Heritage Sites videos #3
description:
This is the third collection of travel video clips about various places around the world that have outstanding natural or cultural value according to the United Nations Educational, Scientific, and Cultural Organization. Not all World Heritage Sites have videos -- for further information, please see http://whc.unesco.org/
